snippet.textDisplay:
First of all, I wish you and your loved ones a Happy New Year.
Then I would love to thank you very much for everything that you have been doing for me personally during 2019!!
While watching this video I was putting on my makeup and guess what? Yes, I used my TATI BEAUTY Eyeshadow Palette and I'm in love with the quality of it, with the colours and the way this palette has been put together! Also, well done on choosing the names for the colours, very classy. Your VOL 1 eyeshadow palette is my first influencer makeup purchases, that's how much I respect and trust you.
I can not wait for your next product ;)
Love from The UK X <3
